705068f-a.title: Brooklyn: Irving Avenue - Suydam Place
705068f-a.text:
Irving Avenue, north side, between Suydam Place and
Willoughby Avenue. Occupying the above site is Public School
No. 123 (right) and the crowd is gathered outside to partake
in Arbor Day exercises. The vlew is west on Irving Avenue.
